# Description
"Eat, drink, and be merry, for tomorrow you may diet".

The Provenders represents all who provide and sell foodstuffs: butchers, bakers, green grocers, dairy, etc. Basically everything between the farm and the kitchen. They meet at the [[landmark/Guildhall of Provenders|Guildhall of Provenders]].

[[person/Gilberto Maggia|Gilberto Maggia]] is head of the guild and one of the five "great guilders" who control much of what happens in Haven (see [[organization/Government of Haven|Government of Haven]]).

